            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x7EA98E2A<!--String: "Cordelia Thebe of Verdemar always had a close relationship with the sea. She settled eventually, but who knows if she'll ever sail away again."--></T>
                  <T>0x9BEA3136<!--String: "The Thebes always seemed like a happy and loving couple. They've been subject to the occasional rumor, but that's to be expected in Ondarion."--></T>
                  <T>0xD26A5E9F<!--String: "The Thebes were always known to be relaxed in their approach to ruling. They never got that strict with the people of Verdemar."--></T>
                  <T>0x7A299751<!--String: "Did you ever meet Cordelia Thebe of Verdemar? She's always been a very adventurous woman, spent many years travelling."--></T>
                  <T>0x4F88D496<!--String: "There were some rumors about Cordelia sneaking out to the lighthouse late at night. Probably a lie, right?"--></T>
                  <T>0x5903FC63<!--String: "The Thebes and the Abrantes are not exactly as close as they look. Everyone knows Cordelia never really liked Ermelinda. I guess Mothers-In-Law can be difficult."--></T>
